com.ephesoft.gxt.systemconfig.client

Interface SystemConfigServiceAsync

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DCMARemoteServiceAsync

    public interface SystemConfigServiceAsync
extends DCMARemoteServiceAsync
    Asynchronous service class to import/export regex pool, import/export table column pool, get list of regex groups and table column pool, get license details.

    1.0.0
    $LastChangedDate:$
    $LastChangedRevision:$
